==English==
===Pronunciation===
/stɑɪl/
===Etymology===
Old English ''[[stiġel]]''
===Noun===
'''stile'''

# a set of [[step]]s [[surmount]]ing a [[fence]], or a narrow [[gate]] or contrived passage through a fence, which in either case allows people but not livestock to pass.
# a [[vertical]] component of a [[panel]] or [[frame]], such as that of a [[door]] or [[window]].
